<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Installation Report for '{{metadata.name}}'</title>
  <link href="../css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <table id="heading">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th colspan="2">
                Stack Information
              </th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="lean" style="vertical-align: top;">Name:</td>
              <td class="content-wrappable">{{metadata.name}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="lean" style="vertical-align: top;">Description:</td>
              <td class="content-wrappable">{{metadata.description}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="lean" style="vertical-align: top;">Version:</td>
              <td class="content-wrappable">{{metadata.version}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="lean">Date Created:</td>
              <td class="content-wrappable">{{metadata.date_created}}</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
        <td id="logo" class="lean">
          <!--<img src="../img/bi_logo_155x43.gif" />-->
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <div id="blueband">&nbsp;</div>

    <h1>Installation Report for '{{metadata.name}}'</h1>

    <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
    <ol class="table-of-contents">
      <li><a href="#introduction">Introduction</a></li>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#introduction-inputs">Inputs</a></li>
        <li><a href="#introduction-outputs">Outputs</a></li>
        <li><a href="#introduction-modules">Modules</a></li>
      </ol>
      <li><a href="#installation">Installation</a></li>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#installation-inputs">Input Values</a></li>
        <li><a href="#installation-outputs">Output Values</a></li>
      </ol>
      <li><a href="#diagnostics-and-testing">Diagnostics and Testing</a></li>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests">Pre-Installation Tests</a></li>
        <ol>
          <li><a href="#diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests-blueprints">Blueprints</a></li>
          <ol>
            {{#each blueprint_test_reports}}
            <li><a href="#diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests-{{name}}">{{name}}</a></li>
            {{/each}}
          </ol>
          <li><a href="#diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests-stack">Stack</a></li>
        </ol>
        <li><a href="#diagnostics-and-testing-post-install-tests">Post-Installation Tests</a></li>
      </ol>
      <li><a href="#conclusion-statement">Conclusion Statement</a></li>
      <li><a href="#definitions-and-abbreviations">Definitions and Abbreviations</a></li>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#definitions">Definitions</a></li>
        <li><a href="#abbreviations">Abbreviations</a></li>
      </ol>
      <li><a href="#reference-documents">Reference Documents</a></li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <h2 id="introduction"><span>1</span>Introduction</h2>

    <p>A <em>Blueprint</em> is a configurable and reusable infrastructure-as-code artefact. Practical examples include foundational infrastructure services, such as compute, networking, and storage, but may as well be of arbitrary higher-level nature, such as an AWS Lambda function.</p>
    <p>A <em>Stack</em> is a composition of reusable Blueprints (potentially in combination with other random infrastructure code) to provide ready-to-use infrastructure for your digital application.</p>

    <p>This document describes the installation of the following stack:</p>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <td class="header lean">Name</td>
        <td>{{metadata.name}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="header lean">Description</td>
        <td>{{metadata.description}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="header lean">Version</td>
        <td>{{metadata.version}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="header lean">URL</td>
        <td>{{metadata.url}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="header lean">Git URL</td>
        <td>{{metadata.git_uri}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="header lean">Plan URL</td>
        <td>tbd.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="header lean">Date Created</td>
        <td>{{metadata.date_created}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Introduction: Inputs -->
    <h3 id="introduction-inputs"><span>1.1</span>Inputs</h3>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
      {{#each terraform_docs.Inputs}}
      <tr>
        <td class="lean">{{Name}}</td>
        <td class="content-wrappable">{{Description}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Introduction: Outputs -->
    <h3 id="introduction-outputs"><span>1.2</span>Outputs</h3>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
      {{#each terraform_docs.Outputs}}
      <tr>
        <td class="lean">{{Name}}</td>
        <td class="content-wrappable">{{Description}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Introduction: Modules -->
    <h3 id="introduction-modules"><span>1.3</span>Modules</h3>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Source</th>
      </tr>
      {{#each terraform_modules}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{Source}} {{Version}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Installation -->
    <h2 id="installation"><span>2</span>Installation</h2>

    <!-- Installation: Input Names/Values -->
    <h3 id="installation-inputs"><span>2.1</span>Input Values</h3>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Value</th>
      </tr>
      {{#each terraform_install.inputs}}
      <tr>
        <td class="lean">{{key}}</td>
        <td class="content-wrappable">{{value}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Installation: Outputs Names/Values -->
    <h3 id="installation-outputs"><span>2.2</span>Output Values</h3>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Value</th>
      </tr>
      {{#each terraform_install.outputs}}
      <tr>
        <td class="lean">{{key}}</td>
        <td class="content-wrappable">{{value.value}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Diagnostics and Testing -->
  <h1 id="diagnostics-and-testing"><span>3</span>Diagnostics and Testing</h1>

  <p>This section documents the results of comparing the actual state of a live stack deployment against a desired state.</p>

  <!-- Diagnostics and Testing: Pre-Install Tests -->
  <h2 id="diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests"><span>3.1</span>Pre-Installation Tests</h2>

  <!-- Diagnostics and Testing: Pre-Install Tests: Blueprints -->
  <h3 id="diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests-blueprints"><span>3.1.1</span>Blueprints</h3>

  <p>The values used to test the following blueprints are for testing purposes only.</p>

  {{#each blueprint_test_reports}}
  <h4 id="diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests-{{name}}">{{name}}</h4>

    {{#each data.inspec.profiles}}
      {{#each controls}}
  <div class="page">
    <h5>{{title}}</h5>
    <p>{{desc}}</p>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Description / Expected Result</th>
        <th class="lean">Start Time</th>
        <th class="lean">Status</th>
      </tr>
        {{#each results}}
      <tr>
        <td class="content-wrappable">{{code_desc}}</td>
        <td class="right">{{start_time}}</td>
        <td class="center">{{status}}</td>
      </tr>
        {{/each}}
    </table>

    <table class="results">
      <tr>
        <td class="lean"><strong>Actual Results</strong></td>
        <td>All tests successful (no deviations or failures).</td>
        <td class="lean">
          <input type="checkbox" checked="checked" /><label>Pass</label><br/>
          <input type="checkbox" disabled="disabled" /><label>Fail</label>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Comments:</strong></td>
        <td colspan="2"><em>n/a</em></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
      {{/each}}
    {{/each}}
  {{/each}}

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Diagnostics and Testing: Pre-Install Tests: Stack -->
    <h3 id="diagnostics-and-testing-pre-install-tests-stack"><span>3.1.2</span>Stack</h3>

    <p>The values used to test the stack are for testing purposes only.</p>

    {{#each inspec.pre-install.profiles}}
      {{#each controls}}
    <h4>{{title}}</h4>
    <p>{{desc}}</p>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Description / Expected Result</th>
        <th class="lean">Start Time</th>
        <th class="lean">Status</th>
      </tr>
        {{#each results}}
      <tr>
        <td class="content-wrappable">{{code_desc}}</td>
        <td class="right">{{start_time}}</td>
        <td class="center">{{status}}</td>
      </tr>
        {{/each}}
    </table>

      {{/each}}
    {{/each}}
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Diagnostics and Testing: Post-Install Tests -->
    <h2 id="diagnostics-and-testing-post-install-tests"><span>3.2</span>Post-Installation Tests</h2>

    {{#each inspec.post-install.profiles}}
      {{#each controls}}
    <h3>{{title}}</h3>
    <p>{{desc}}</p>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Description / Expected Result</th>
        <th class="lean">Start Time</th>
        <th class="lean">Status</th>
      </tr>
        {{#each results}}
      <tr>
        <td class="content-wrappable">{{code_desc}}</td>
        <td class="right">{{start_time}}</td>
        <td class="center">{{status}}</td>
      </tr>
        {{/each}}
    </table>

      {{/each}}
    {{/each}}

    <table class="results">
      <tr>
        <td class="lean"><strong>Actual Results</strong></td>
        <td>All tests successful (no deviations or failures).</td>
        <td class="lean">
          <input type="checkbox" checked="checked" /><label>Pass</label><br/>
          <input type="checkbox" disabled="disabled" /><label>Fail</label>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Comments:</strong></td>
        <td colspan="2"><em>n/a</em></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Conclusion Statement -->
    <h1 id="conclusion-statement"><span>4</span>Conclusion Statement</h1>

    <p>All deliverables of the Technical Installation Plan have been successfully executed and the signature of this Report verifies that
the system has been installed according to all requirements stated in the Installation Plan or, in the event the requirements
are not met, that the deviations and/or failures are properly documented and addressed.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <!-- Definitions and Abbreviations -->
    <h1 id="definitions-and-abbreviations"><span>5</span>Definitions and Abbreviations</h1>

    <!-- Definitions and Abbreviations: Definitions -->
    <h2 id="definitions"><span>5.1</span>Definitions</h2>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <th class="lean">Term</th>
        <th>Definition</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Git</td>
        <td class="content-wrappable">A distributed version control system, e.g., Bitbucket, GitHub, and GitLab.</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Definitions and Abbreviations: Abbreviations -->
    <h2 id="abbreviations"><span>5.2</span>Abbreviations</h2>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <th class="lean">Abbreviation</th>
        <th>Meaning</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>URL</td>
        <td class="content-wrappable">A uniform resource locator (URL) is the address of a resource on the Internet.</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>See <a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/general/latest/gr/glos-chap.html">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/general/latest/gr/glos-chap.html</a> for a list of AWS-specific definitions and abbreviations.</p>

    <!-- Reference Documents -->
    <h1 id="reference-documents"><span>6</span>Reference Documents</h2>

    <table>
      <tr>
        <th class="lean">Document ID</th>
        <th style="width: 100%;">Name</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="right"><em>n/a</em></td>
        <td><em>n/a</em></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
